{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/contact/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"3757f665-3cb8-58fa-8711-f518bf732565","html":"<p>Have any questions or just wanna say hello? Feel free to shoot me over <a href=\"mailto:jhyeun@uwaterloo.ca\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">an email</a>.</p>\n<p>Not really an email kind of person? Contact me through <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthew-hyeun/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a> or even <a href=\"https://github.com/mhyeun\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a> if you somehow manage to find a way to.</p>\n<p>Looking forward to hearing from you.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/d2602/contact_photo.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/8ac56/contact_photo.webp 240w,\n/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/d3be9/contact_photo.webp 480w,\n/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/e46b2/contact_photo.webp 960w,\n/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/f992d/contact_photo.webp 1440w,\n/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/882b9/contact_photo.webp 1920w,\n/static/2f4b00259c37cc5260585bb898cffa07/b33a3/contact_photo.webp 4032w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n         